Mythbuster: COVID-19 virus can be transmitted in areas with hot and humid climates
From the evidence so far, the COVID-19 virus can be transmitted in ALL AREAS, including areas with hot and humid weather. Regardless of climate, adopt protective measures https://t.co/rq7ZO6oTz1 https://t.co/UD37ePH09H
